    "3. **Model Training** - Train YOLO model with optimized settings\n",
    "4. **Evaluation** - Validate and test the trained model\n",
    "\n",
    "## Requirements:\n",
    "- Python scripts: `dataset_utils.py`, `train.py`\n",
    "- Configuration file: `config.yaml`\n",
